'''BRAL is a city movement striving to make Brussels sustainable.'''

URL: http://www.bral.brussels/

=== Description ===

"Along with their members and partners, BRAL wants to build an environmentally friendly and affordable city in Brussels. They organise actions, lobbies, supports citizens' initiatives and provides advice to the authorities. Their priorities today are: better air quality, an economy that is both green and social, and an  efficient city development with room for participation."


